    {
        "content": "<p>I'm more surprised that it worked in v4.28.0! Btw, <code>set_option backward.isDefEq.respectTransparency false in</code> fixes it.<br>\nTurns out it was able to derive <code>Std.LawfulBEqOrd Unit</code> and then directly <code>Std.ReflOrd Unit</code> before (note that <code>instance : Std.ReflOrd Unit := inferInstance</code> also worked before)</p>",
